UID:934cfe0bcecc899b590fab37d1920a5e@montclairfilm.org
DESCRIPTION:After prison\, a woman attempts to reconnect with her young da
 ughter but faces resistance from everyone except a bar owner with ties to 
 her child. As they grow closer\, she must confront her past mistakes to bu
 ild a hopeful future.
LOCATION:Clairidge Cinema 2\, 486 Bloomfield Avenue\, Montclair\, NJ 07042
URL:https://montclairfilm.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FRk
